Changes
/////////////////////////////////////////////

v1.0 - last release on this branch

v0.9c - Removed	TreePM and direct summation options. Added ability to use precomputed
        lensing planes. 

v0.9b - Added TreePM (broken) and direct summation (broken) options. Fixed bug in domain 
        decomp. - April 2013

v0.9a - fixed bug which outputs the zero-th component of the deflection 
        angle twice - found by Wei Chengliang in binary ray output - January 2013

v0.9 - original release - October 2012

